#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.6-35B-A3B.md:5
msgid ""
"Qwen3.6-35B-A3B is a sparse MoE model in the Qwen3.6 family. It has 35B "
"total parameters with about 3B activated per token, and uses the same "
"hybrid attention architecture (GDN + full attention) as Qwen3.5. "
"Deployment on vLLM Ascend follows the same pattern as other Qwen3.5-style"
" MoE models."
msgstr ""
"Qwen3.6-35B-A3B是Qwen3.6系列中的稀疏MoE模型。总参数量为35B，每个token激活约3B参数，采用与Qwen3.5相同的混合注意力架构（GDN+全注意力）。在vLLM Ascend上的部署方式与其他Qwen3.5风格MoE模型一致。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.6-35B-A3B.md:7
msgid ""
"This document covers supported features, environment setup, single-node "
"deployment, and accuracy/performance evaluation."
msgstr ""
"本文档涵盖支持特性、环境配置、单节点部署以及精度/性能评估。"

